So I went to Va to take care of my Grandmother for like a week & when I got back I got to see my baby... Even just hearing her voice makes me smile... Okay, folks... make the discusting *gushy noise* I've earned it.

I think she got tired of me jumpin' up & sqeezing her arm. Anywho, after that she got me a really cute wig *shhh don't tell anyone*, but yeah my head is getting all fuzzy from shaving it & well sometimes I just wanna be a girl... a really girlie girl... cause it's fun to have *MEN*  turn their heads at me, I kind of missed that attention (even though I am not attracted to guys, it still can be fun to have them all hot & bothered by me)  So after that we went to get some Mexican food & the waitress was like "can I get you a margita" (it's funny how different I look with some heels, a dress, & lil wig. Har. *big toothy grin*) So we came home & were thinking about going to Alyssa's, because you know- -I have an evil, fat old Ma' & I just knew that she'd ruin our night- -And that she did, when she came home all she could do was yell & she didn't even *gasp* say anything about my wig! The nerve of her! So we went down stairs & I boo hooed, but soon the boo hooing turned to laughter & the laughter turned to being scared of the Exorcist all over again. (Damn that Jackie) Then she went home, cause the fat one *affectionately known as mom* said she couldn't sleep over & she was getting tired. The liqour is still sittin' in the basement, waitin' for Jackie to come & drink it.

So yeah, it wasn't long after she left that I started crying & being a dumb little kid, crying for my lost childhood. I know, *Boo Hoo* So I just started looking for something that I thought would make me feel better & sure enough, I found it... Only it all it did was make deleriously stupid. So I called Alyssa & didn't tell her what I did at all, just focussed on the highlights of my day... Then my friend, Joey saw me online & asked me if I wanted to do anything, immediately I asked him if he wanted to go up to Towson to suprise Alyssa, so he picked me up & I was all excited... on the way we were talking about how we were going to sing Xmas Carol's on her door step, but instead... I did the stalkerish thing & just tapped on her bed room window... I really tried to play off the whole being fucked up thing with her, it worked for Joey, but she's seen me drunk too many times & I just seemed like  a different person... I was an ass... made her all worried... Then we just talked for a while & suddenly I somehow managed my whole stupid silly high. I LOVE her.

We left after about an hour, Joey got called to a house fire (he's a firefighter & a republican, yuck!) I saw someone there that I'd rather forget, but thankfully she was too preoccupied with the fire to notice that I was there. We watched the house disengrate & it felt like a nice lil campfire.

Okay... after I went home I didn't fall asleep untill about 6 or 7 (which is not too unusual for me, but still I'm blaming it on that damn movie)

And there we have it yesterday was wonderful in alot of ways, Muh Jackie   really sweet to me, My Alyssa helped me focus... My day was full of Laughter & tears... How on earth could that EVER be a bad day?

Well, I'm done hurting anyone's eyes that has read this...
